# Formspree form ID for the contact form (Let's Talk section).
# 1. Sign up at https://formspree.io
# 2. Create a new form and set notification email to: adhiyantverma00623@gmail.com
# 3. Copy your form ID from the form endpoint (e.g. from https://formspree.io/f/xyzabc → xyzabc)
# 4. Copy this file to .env and set the value:
VITE_FORMSPREE_FORM_ID=your_formspree_form_id
